msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/airstrike"
msgid "IL-2 Airstrike"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/date"
msgid "March 13th, 1945 · Outskirts of Sarajevo, Yugoslavia"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/music"
msgid "Play music (loudspeaker)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/music_hint"
msgid "The loudspeaker on the Sherman can be used to raise the morale of our troops by playing music."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/name"
msgid "Yugoslavian Heroes"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/name_big"
msgid "Yugoslavian Heroes"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/fighter/00"
msgid "Well, the weather turned out nice today. Everyone is out and about, not a single fascist or villager has noticed us coming."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/fighter/01"
msgid "The trucks are all going to the center of town. Too many fascists."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/fighter/02"
msgid "You have a death wish. The Germans are retreating. We want them gone, but don't have to kill them; they will run away soon enough. What are you playing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/fighter/03"
msgid "Tiger! A bloody Tiger! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/fighter/04"
msgid "Tigers are on the menu today! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/fighter/05"
msgid "So, comrade tank commander, what secret weapon do you have to catch the Tigers from behind, huh? Maybe we can all be blown to pieces as bait while you get your shit together?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/fighter/06"
msgid "Is that solid gold? And they've hoarded truckloads of that in town? How are we going to get it out?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/fighter/07"
msgid "That is... a lot of gold!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/fighter/08"
msgid "The trucks have arrived, we will begin loading them. The warehouse needs protecting until we're all done."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/fighter/09"
msgid "Fascists incoming! Comrades, defend the trucks!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/fighter/10"
msgid "Well comrades, I have the distinct sensation that the war ends here and now for me. I hope not to see you again too soon, but it was an honor to liberate the motherland with you all these years."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/01"
msgid "Yup, but the Germans are all over the place. Trucks are going in but not coming out. Something about this stinks! We need to find out what the fascists are hoarding here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/02"
msgid "Hmm. It looks like one of those trucks broke down up ahead. I say we take a look at their cargo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/03"
msgid "My friend, this goes beyond liberating our country from the fascist yoke. The Germans are taking valuables with them. This particular convoy seems heavily protected."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/04"
msgid "Heads up, dead north! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/05"
msgid "Don't panic. The Tigers are vulnerable in close quarters. We'll outflank them and attack them from behind. Whatever they are safeguarding in this town must be very valuable if tigers are strolling around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/06"
msgid "Well, well. Now that's something worth guarding with Tigers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/07"
msgid "Comrade, do you know anyone who can help us extract these valuables?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/08"
msgid "I checked the documents in the vehicle and they were heading towards the farmers' warehouse in the center of town. It makes sense; it's a large building. That is where we will find our treasure. Let's move out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/09"
msgid "Yeah, well, this gold is useless unless we can get it out of here. The Germans clearly want to take it with them, so we need to act swiftly. Secure the village! Comrade tank commander, call your friends up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/10"
msgid "Comrades, I need a thorough search. I don't want a single fascist left in this village compromising our operation. We need those trucks coming in safe and sound."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/11"
msgid "Damn it! We failed to clear the town!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/12"
msgid "Comrades, set up a defensive perimeter around the warehouse! The gold will take time to load, and the Germans will want it back!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/13"
msgid "No! We've lost too many transport trucks!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/14"
msgid "Spread out and take ambush positions!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/15"
msgid "We don't have supplies. I wonder whether we should look out for German supply convoys. At least one of them will be bound to be retreating westward."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/16"
msgid "Comrade tank commander. The uniforms and the weaponry, I do understand. But is there a particular reason to take a Tiger tank with you too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/leader/17"
msgid "The fuel system is junk. It smells of fuel a mile away. The transmission is falling to pieces. You have no spare parts and huge German markings to attract friendly fire!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/01"
msgid "Now then. Tell me, comrades, what's on the menu today? How can the glorious Red Army be of assistance?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/02"
msgid "Oh man... nobody said anything about them Tigers!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/03"
msgid "Always with the pessimistic attitude, Iosif... I'll tell you what we do. We have a loudspeaker, and when we go into battle, we like to play music very loud... it kind of calms us down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/04"
msgid "Alright, let's find out what those Fascists have got. My guys here in the back are ready."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/05"
msgid "Comrade Partisan, Always with the pessimistic attitude. Can't you enjoy the fact you just became rich? Why don't you let me organise a pickup?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/06"
msgid "Sure thing. Let's find out where the Fascists keep the gold, clear the area, and I'm sure I could persuade some comrades to come along with transports. The war has been very tough on all of us. The thought of returning to the Urals emptyhanded seems rather sad, you know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/07"
msgid "Yes, Comrade..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/08"
msgid "(on radio) Gav-gav, gav-gav!!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/09"
msgid "(on radio) No, I'm not trying to be funny. Listen, I need a favour. How soon can you come here with, say... 10 empty trucks?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/10"
msgid "(on radio) Listen, I need you here round about now, I'm about to cut you into a very good deal, if you don't want it, then you're out, I can find 10 trucks almost anywhere."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/11"
msgid "Yeah, just as I thought. Alright, comrades, listen up! 6 minutes for our trucks to come from the southeast, secure the town!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/12"
msgid "Alright, comrades, I have gotten us some air support over my portable radio. It seems our air force guys have nothing better to do than accept tasking from a low-life tank driver."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/13"
msgid "Alright, here goes nothing, let's see what our planes can do!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/14"
msgid "Calling in an airstrike!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/15"
msgid "Calling in an IL-2. One thousand seven hundred horsepowers of goodness and some big bombs strapped under it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/16"
msgid "Hm. Definitely an anti-social type."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/17"
msgid "It is a beautiful tank."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/narrator/tanker/18"
msgid "Why is everyone so damn negative around here? Can't we just take a moment to delight ourselves with the prize we have collected?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/outro_completed"
msgid "Great job! Who would ever have thought you’d emerge a millionaire? This victory is proof that you should never let them negative waves win."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/outro_failed"
msgid "What happened? Did you not watch the 1970 movie Kelly’s Heroes? Watch it, and try again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/place"
msgid "Elements of the Yugoslav People's Liberation Army"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/story"
msgid "It’s 1945, and the Germans are retreating from Yugoslavia. \nHaving lost the easier withdrawal route through Serbia, they secure the more difficult passage through Kosovo, Sandzak, and Bosnia. They even score a series of temporary successes against the People's Liberation Army. \nIn early March, the Germans move troops from southern Bosnia to support an unsuccessful counter-offensive in Hungary, enabling the People’s Liberation Army to attack the weakened German positions.  \nToday, you are looking for Germans while driving through the beautiful Yugoslavian landscape. \nWhatever you do or find, just make sure you avoid them negative waves, and you’ll be fine.\n\nGood luck!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/task1"
msgid "Inspect the broken-down vehicle to find what the Germans are transporting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/task2"
msgid "Secure the warehouse containing the gold."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/task3"
msgid "Clear the village of Germans so the transports can safely come in to collect the gold."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/task4"
msgid "Protect the trucks from German counter-attacks while the gold is being loaded. At least 5 trucks must survive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/task_opt_sherman"
msgid "Keep the Sherman operational."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/task_secret"
msgid "Secret objective #1"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/task_secret_completed"
msgid "Secret objective #1: Intercept and capture the supply truck"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/timer1"
msgid "The transport column will arrive in:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/timer2"
msgid "Time remaining to load the gold:"
msgstr ""

#, boost-format
msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1945_04_yugoslavia/trucks"
msgid "%1% transport trucks operational. "
msgstr ""
